化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"75ea20d60cab42ab997c5795fc1dc7743e7948bf","tid":1666942,"uid":95445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"香港人 還拖"},{"pid":"a0b7ae6308d76e44a41340fd9dba99b2ce7a59ba","tid":1666942,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55e5601e49b325cc7016a1c4d2882f1e21184620","tid":1666942,"uid":164166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:52:22.000Z","msg":"結果真係造成咗民間巨大嘅反撲 歷史嘅echo真係無可避免<br />\n當年嘅兩人組而家天各一方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec161373094bc00a8b026c2672d221d14b55bf42","tid":1666942,"uid":217483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"推下先&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"3b8f84a177bcd73a32527b661264be6a32586425","tid":1666942,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏嘅同我入嚟<br />\n快啲把握最好時機</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b6667594474f8396aa30dc7861a8c305759e718","tid":1666942,"uid":95445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"香港人 還拖"},{"pid":"cf67ad1528ec09d4c56bf8db5adb95d47f9b37ac","tid":1666942,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:00:08.000Z","msg":"有邊個香港網台曾經畀後生仔發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（唔准計MyRadio）"},{"pid":"c4521d02f9676de31cbefdf8bcab5d6ea4a239e5","tid":1666942,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"又唔好講佢幾年前講嘅野放喺今日個時勢到<br />\n佢講嘅野都唔一定啱"},{"pid":"89e8879252febaecd70bf97fbc939068f31f3f9b","tid":1666942,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"57462ee824607ac70f34034bce56611416ace76a","tid":1666942,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n此風不可長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐監好撚差咪撚制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}